of underground pipes --

00:01:32.472 --> 00:01:34.540
has been severely damaged.

00:01:35.116 --> 00:01:38.276
And while the water quality
is slowly improving

00:01:38.300 --> 00:01:40.351
and the pipes are being replaced now,

00:01:40.375 --> 00:01:42.075
more than two years later,

00:01:42.099 --> 00:01:44.449
the water is still not safe to drink.

00:01:46.276 --> 00:01:49.161
So, people are still in shock.

00:01:49.185 --> 00:01:50.493
